trans-unit.source: Represents a stack trace, which is an ordered collection of one or more stack frames.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en stakksporing som en sortert samling av én eller flere stakken for forhandleren.

trans-unit.source: StackTrace information will be most informative with Debug build configurations.
trans-unit.target: StackTrace informasjonen vil være mest informativ med Debug build-konfigurasjoner.

trans-unit.source: By default, Debug builds include debug symbols, while Release builds do not.
trans-unit.target: Som standard inneholde feilsøking delversjoner feilsøking symboler, mens versjonen delversjoner ikke.

trans-unit.source: The debug symbols contain most of the file, method name, line number, and column information used in constructing <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame> and StackTrace objects.
trans-unit.target: Feilsøking symbolene inneholder de fleste av filen, metodenavnet, linjenummer og kolonneinformasjon som brukes i konstruere <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame>og StackTrace objekter.</xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame>

trans-unit.source: StackTrace might not report as many method calls as expected, due to code transformations that occur during optimization.
trans-unit.target: StackTrace kan ikke rapportere så mange metodekall som forventet på grunn av feilkoden transformeringer som oppstår under optimalisering.

trans-unit.source: Use the returned <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame> array to enumerate and examine function calls in the <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackTrace>.
trans-unit.target: Bruk den returnerte <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame>matrisen slik liste, og Undersøk funksjonskall i <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackTrace>.</xref:System.Diagnostics.StackTrace> </xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame>

trans-unit.source: The length of the returned array is equal to the <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackTrace.FrameCount%2A> property value.
trans-unit.target: Lengden på den returnerte matrisen er lik den <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackTrace.FrameCount%2A>egenskapsverdi.</xref:System.Diagnostics.StackTrace.FrameCount%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame> array elements are in reverse chronological order.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame>matriseelementene er i omvendt kronologisk.</xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame> at array index 0 represents the most recent function call in the stack trace and the last frame pushed onto the call stack.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame>i matrisen representerer indeksen 0 siste funksjonskallet i stakksporingen og den siste rammen som er sendt inn kallstakken.</xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame> at array index <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackTrace.FrameCount%2A> minus 1 represents the oldest function call in the stack trace and the first frame pushed onto the call stack.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame>på matriseindeksen <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackTrace.FrameCount%2A>minus 1 representerer eldste funksjonskallet i stakksporet og første rammen sendt inn kallstakken.</xref:System.Diagnostics.StackTrace.FrameCount%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame>

trans-unit.source: Use the GetFrames method to obtain all stack frames in a stack trace; use the <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackTrace.GetFrame%2A> method to obtain a specific stack frame in a stack trace.
trans-unit.target: Bruk GetFrames-metoden til å hente alle stakk forhandleren i stakksporing; Bruk av <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackTrace.GetFrame%2A>metode for å hente en bestemt stakk ramme i en stakksporing.</xref:System.Diagnostics.StackTrace.GetFrame%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame> indexes are ordered alike by the two methods.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame>Indekser sorteres alike av to måter.</xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame> at index 0 in the array returned by GetFrames is equivalent to the <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame> returned by <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackTrace.GetFrame%2A> with an input index of 0.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel den <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame>ved indeksen 0 i matrisen som returneres av GetFrames tilsvarer den <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame>returnert av <xref:System.Diagnostics.StackTrace.GetFrame%2A>med en inndata indeksen 0.</xref:System.Diagnostics.StackTrace.GetFrame%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame> </xref:System.Diagnostics.StackFrame>
